            <fr:taxon>Proof</fr:taxon>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
 <html:p>This is immediate, using the unit map of <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-0028.xml" title="Propositional truncation" addr="forest://erct/erct-0028" type="local">propositional truncation</fr:link> and the <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-000U.xml" title="Biinverse" addr="forest://erct/erct-000U" type="local">section</fr:link> of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f]]></fr:tex>.</html:p>
</fr:mainmatter>
